invalid type: string "RAG Evaluation Benchmarking Tool\n\nThis tool evaluates Retrieval-Augmented Generation pipelines using\nLLM-as-a-Judge methodology. It supports four evaluation metrics:\nfaithfulness, answer relevance, context precision, and correctness.\n\nThe system uses Google Gemini as both the RAG model and the evaluation\njudge. ChromaDB is used as the vector store for document storage.